{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d27840fe-2d08-4e79-8642-13d83d66a027","content":"Here's the correct skip attribute for each framework:\n\n| Framework | Attribute | Example |\n|-----------|-----------|---------|\n| **MSTest** | `[Ignore]` | `[Ignore(\"Blocked by bug #123\")]` |\n| **xUnit** | `Skip` on `[Fact]`/`[Theory]` | `[Fact(Skip = \"Blocked by bug #123\")]` |\n| **NUnit** | `[Ignore]` | `[Ignore(\"Blocked by bug #123\")]` |\n| **TUnit** | `[Skip]` | `[Skip(\"Blocked by bug #123\")]` |\n\n**Key differences:**\n- **xUnit** is the outlier — skip is a *property* on the test attribute, not a separate attribute.\n- **MSTest & NUnit** look the same (`[Ignore]`) but come from different namespaces (`Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting` vs `NUnit.Framework`).\n- **TUnit** uses `[Skip]` instead of `[Ignore]`.\n\nAll four support a reason string so the skip shows up in test reports.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7a1e6743-6dce-48d4-abe2-8c234d285677","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about the correct attributes to skip tests with a reason message in MSTest, xUnit, NUnit, and TUnit. This is a knowledge question about .NET test frameworks. I have a relevant skill - `dotnet-test-frameworks` which provides reference data for .NET test framework skip annotations and other patterns. Let me invoke it.\n\nActually, looking at the skill description more carefully: \"Reference data for .NET test framework detection patterns, assertion APIs, skip annotations, setup/teardown methods, and common test smell indicators across MSTest, xUnit, NUnit, and TUnit.\" This is exactly what's needed.\n\nBut the skill says \"DO NOT USE directly — loaded by test analysis skills\". However, the user is asking specifically about skip annotations across all four frameworks. \n\nI can answer this directly from my knowledge - MSTest and NUnit use `[Ignore(\"reason\")]`, xUnit uses `[Fact(Skip = \"reason\")]` or `[Theory(Skip = \"reason\")]`, and TUnit uses `[Skip(\"reason\")]`.","outputTokens":557,"requestId":"981E:3B4A47:1C2A09:24A469:69FFDC79"},"id":"ac64e88c-8781-435c-be3e-603689b8c586","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:16:54.350Z","parentId":"7c244cd0-78c7-4e61-af68-c7499df9fd65"}
